divs: Sighting DetailsAround 4:30 in the morning I saw the backside of a rectangular shaped object as it passed over my apartment building . It was traveling east to west in a straight line and the height was between 150 to 300 feet . When it passed by or over the building I could hear a hum other than that there was no engine sounds or jet sounds . Five bright white lights across the back side of it and a red light . It was strobing with some of the white lites doing a double flash , like blip blib every 10 secounds or so . The size was about 30 to 50 feet across the back side if not longer . I had it in sight for about a minute and a half untill it faded out of sight in the distance . I did a drawing on my pc of what I saw , sorry the drawing is crude I did it with my mouse . This is the fifth time since January that my girlfriend and I have seen something over the river here .
